						<summary>

						<p>On a slab lying in the Śiva temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>Kākatīya: Gaṇapatidēva.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1134, Āṅgīrasa, Vaiśākha, śu. 3, Thursday, corresponding to 1212 A.D., April 6.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records the gift of land in the village Neḍukuḍi to the temple of Muktīśvara Mahādēva by Rudrabōya for the merit of his parents and the king.</p>						

						</summary>
